Beacon v0.4.01
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Installation is a no-brainer. 

1. Just copy the `editor' folder to your `htdocs' directory. 

2. Get a snack.

3. Point your browser to the editor folder (eg. http://youdomainname.com/editor/)

4. You're all good to go!

Note: To add plugins and configuring beacon at your website ping us at #beacon (freenode) or wait for the HOW TO soon. ;-)
